languages.text: "Нас наняли убивать мон-кай. Тебя? Или ты приш{mf|ел|ла} сказать, кого?"
"We were hired to kill a mon-keigh. Is it you? Or have you come to tell us who it is?"
languages.original_text: "Нас наняли убивать мон-кай. Тебя? Или ты приш{mf|ел|ла} сказать, кого?"

languages.text: “有人雇我们来杀一只猴子，是你吗？或者说，你知道那只猴子是谁吗？”
languages.original_text: "We were hired to kill a mon-keigh. Is it you? Or have you come to tell us who it is?"

traits.locale_text: “有人雇我们来杀一只猴子，是你吗？或者，你知道那个人是谁吗？”

languages.text: 「俺らはモン＝ケイを倒すために雇われたんだ。雇い主はお前か？それか、誰が雇い主なのか告げに来たのか？」
languages.original_text: "We were hired to kill a mon-keigh. Is it you? Or have you come to tell us who it is?"

traits.locale_text: 「俺らはモン＝ケイを倒すために雇われたんだ。雇い主はお前か？それか、誰が雇い主なのか告げに来たのか？」

languages.text: «Nos contrataron para matar a {mf|un|una} mon-keigh. ¿Se trata de usted? ¿O ha venido a decirnos quién es?».
languages.original_text: "We were hired to kill a mon-keigh. Is it you? Or have you come to tell us who it is?"

traits.locale_text: «Nos contrataron para matar a {mf|un|una} mon-keigh. ¿Se trata de usted? ¿O ha venido a decir quién es?».

languages.text: "Wir wurden angeheuert, um einen Chem-Pan-Sey zu töten. Seid Ihr das? Oder seid Ihr gekommen, um uns zu sagen, wer es ist?"
languages.original_text: "We were hired to kill a mon-keigh. Is it you? Or have you come to tell us who it is?"

traits.locale_text: "Wir wurden angeheuert, um einen Chem-Pan-Sey zu töten. Seid Ihr das? Oder seid Ihr gekommen, um uns zu sagen, wer es ist?"

languages.text: « On nous a embauchés pour tuer {mf|un|une} mon-keigh. C'est vous ? Ou alors, vous êtes là pour nous dire qui est notre cible ? »
languages.original_text: "We were hired to kill a mon-keigh. Is it you? Or have you come to tell us who it is?"

traits.locale_text: « On nous a embauchés pour tuer {mf|un|une} mon-keigh. C'est vous ? Ou alors, vous êtes là pour nous dire qui est notre cible ? »

languages.text: "Bir mon-keigh'i öldürmek için tutulduk. Sen misin o? Ya da bize onun kim olduğunu söylemeye mi geldin?"
